Text.val: 12.02.2014 JH SCR18705 Added update of DEBC_REINSURANCECONTRACT
10.02.2014 JH SCR18700 Added update of DEBC_GRADE_AMOUNT

SQL_STMT_U.val: update :1/DEBC set DEBC_REINSURANCECODE = '', DEBC_REINSURANCENUMBER = '', DEBC_REINSURANCELIM = null, DEBC_REINSURANCELIMCURR = '', DEBC_REINSURANCELIMSTART = null, DEBC_REINSURANCELIMEXPIRY = null, DEBC_REINSURANCEREPORTDAYS = 0, DEBC_REINSURANCETYPE = 0, DEBC_REINSURANCEGRADE = '' where DEBC_DATDELETED is null

select A.DRIH_DEBH_NO, A.DRIH_ADMNO, A.DRIH_CLNTNO, max(A.DRIH_DATSTARTING) from :1/DRIH A where exists(select * from :1/DEBC where DEBC_ADMNO = A.DRIH_ADMNO and DEBC_CLNTNO = A.DRIH_CLNTNO and DEBC_DEBH = A.DRIH_DEBH_NO and DEBC_DATDELETED is null) group by A.DRIH_DEBH_NO, A.DRIH_ADMNO, A.DRIH_CLNTNO order by A.DRIH_DEBH_NO, A.DRIH_ADMNO, A.DRIH_CLNTNO
